ce src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092710/extras/2fd42aa9f5ee450de28daf9e061b0820.webm?t=1766144700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092710/extras/2fd42aa9f5ee450de28daf9e061b0820.mp4?t=1766144700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>A rich narrative in an enchanted forest</strong><br><br>Explore an enchanted land filled with friendly creatures. In the forest, new surprises await behind each tree. Adventure is just waiting for you.  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092710/extras/dde9c9573bcd4003880f1c540767bb8d.poster.avif?t=1766144700\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092710/extras/dde9c9573bcd4003880f1c540767bb8d.webm?t=1766144700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092710/extras/dde9c9573bcd4003880f1c540767bb8d.mp4?t=1766144700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>An interactive story</strong><br><br>Your actions matter and will impact the narrative. They shape your journey and will ultimately decide the path you want to take. As you explore this new world, forge your own story.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092710/extras/ff0127d920654bd8385b68461dd34993.poster.avif?t=1766144700\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092710/extras/ff0127d920654bd8385b68461dd34993.webm?t=1766144700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3092710/extras/ff0127d920654bd8385b6